clanbomber: clanbomber (Bomberman-like multiplayer game that uses ClanLib)
clanbomber:
clanbomber: ClanBomber is a free (GPL) Bomberman-like multiplayer game that uses
clanbomber: ClanLib, a free multi platform C++ game SDK. First "ClanBomber" was
clanbomber: only a working title for a small game started in September 1998, that
clanbomber: has only been started to learn how to use ClanLib. But the ClanBomber
clanbomber: project has grown into a real game. It is fully playable and features
clanbomber: Computer controlled bombers, however, it is recommended to play
clanbomber: ClanBomber with friends (3-8 players are really fun).
clanbomber: http://clanbomber.sourceforge.net/
